<title>抖音电商的三道“选择题”</title>
<link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzcxNTgxOQ==&mid=2247645325&idx=1&sn=12dd4e444224245aa0e46f96877b74e6&chksm=fa77a409cd002d1fcd1c15ec52b2c3a371dfe7c3c61f7be43aec1213e93b6443d43d3016f260&scene=58&subscene=0#rd</link>
<description>低价还是GMV？达播还是店播？直播电商还是货架电商？</description>
