34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">奔驰也意识到，中国消费者对豪华车的需求与欧美市场有显著差异，尤其是对后排空间的极高要求。在洞察这一趋势后，奔驰在第九代E级车上推出了长轴距版本，轴距的增加带来了显著的后排腿部空间提升，舒适度提升十分明显。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="370" data-backw="561" data-imgfileid="513563566" data-ratio="0.6601851851851852" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=f23da408&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOaFsUa11r0CZtM0AyZE2LUiaTDn3LZHGPNHKSnGYodNRA6I4NSlHKITLDBd5ialm7ZwmYw2okVAkofhQVmNicv4qg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">从设计上来看，增加轴距常常会让车身比例显得笨重或拖沓，而奔驰E级通过巧妙的设计语言，保持了优雅的车身轮廓，使长轴距版车型依然具备行政级轿车应有的气场与流畅线条，这也是其在产品设计造诣上的侧面体现。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">在2024年推出的第11代E级长轴距车型，进一步提升后排空间和内饰豪华感，满足中国消费者“老板座驾”的场景需求。超10项中国专属后排豪华舒适增配，如头等舱般的座椅调节和源自迈巴赫的后排三角窗，堪称行业翘楚。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="374" data-backw="561" data-imgfileid="513563573" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=d5548516&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOaFsUa11r0CZtM0AyZE2LUiaTDn3LZHGPQzsxAsu2OWYia08R6mibw9xUFVnFoDVI9RpKLWkj4O20zxkIcszlEsgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">总之，奔驰E级的长轴距设计并不仅仅是这件事本身，更是通过精细的工程设计，让空间的每一寸都被合理利用，同时也创造了一种“宽敞不仅是舒适，更是一种身份象征”的价值标签。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">以前，长轴距只在顶级豪华车型中出现，而奔驰E级将其普及到行政级豪华轿车中，直接带动了整个市场的“加长热潮”，在奔驰E级推出长轴距版后，其他品牌也纷纷跟进，将长轴距版车型视为打开中国市场的标配，而这一切的开端，正是奔驰E级当时率先尝试的结果。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">现在回过头来看，这种“因地制宜”的产品策略彻底改变了中国消费者对豪华轿车的认知，“轴距的延伸”，说到底则是对中国市场与用户需求的深度洞察。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">为了更加贴近中国消费者，奔驰将本土化研发提到了战略高度。过去五年，奔驰在中国市场的研发投入累计超过105亿元人民币，建立了覆盖电动化、智能化、自动驾驶等多个领域的研发中心。这不仅让奔驰能够迅速响应中国消费者的需求，也使中国成为奔驰全球创新的重要一环。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">奔驰在中国还进行了许多“接地气”的创新。比如针对中国复杂的泊车环境，优化了新一代智能泊车的识别精度；始终“以驾驶者为主导”的L2+导航辅助驾驶，覆盖高速与城市快速路段，包含自动变道、自动远离大车等L2+智驾功能，系统不会跟驾驶者抢方向盘，不会凌驾于驾驶者之上，打造安心好用的“人机共驾”体验。这些创新不仅让奔驰E级更贴近用户，也让消费者感受到了一种“量身定制”的尊重。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">十几年过去，奔驰也用实际行动证明了一件事：想赢得中国消费者的心，不光要努力，还得特别懂“国情”，而中国专属也不仅是一句口号，更是一份承诺。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><h2 style="margin-right: 0.5em;margin-left: 0.5em;text-align: center;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;"><o:p><span style="font-size: 17px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(171, 25, 66);"><span style="font-size: 17px;outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体, SimSun;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">一直“被对标”</span></strong></span></o:p></h2><h2 style="margin-right: 0.5em;margin-left: 0.5em;text-align: center;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;"><o:p><span style="font-size: 17px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(171, 25, 66);"><span style="font-size: 17px;outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体, SimSun;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">是挑战更是认可</span></strong></span></o:p></h2><h2 style="margin-right: 0.5em;margin-left: 0.5em;text-align: center;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-fileid="513381045" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="513563571" data-ratio="0.04372842347525892" data-s="300,640" style="margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-indent: 0em;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;display: inline;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" data-type="png" data-w="869" src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=33dacf16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOaFsUa11r0Aibict80r8B3FAPhjUxwC86rR7HhKicIc2liaXJg9KKUtS6lRbyOicFQ5MWUfh1cCnMvlJHiaoVyTyRkNQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic"/><br/></h2><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">从市场开拓者到时代领跑者，奔驰E级车用77年的时间诠释了何谓“豪华”，不仅在于它对技术、设计、体验的执着追求，更在于它始终站在时代的前沿，敢于挑战市场的认知极限。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">历经11代进化，奔驰E级在全球已经累计交付超过1600万辆，千万用户的选择本身就是绝佳证明。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="374" data-backw="561" data-imgfileid="513563568" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=2225067e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOaFsUa11r0CZtM0AyZE2LUiaTDn3LZHGPfuS5If5VYbTQpjVcvuO6FKeibURwNkVTA8QvF0btdMoic3AgeD5YGbWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">奔驰E级车之所以“被对标”，也是因为它定义了一个时代的标杆；之所以“无法超越”，是因为它从未停止超越自己。从安全标准的树立到当今的数字豪华座舱，从1947年的豪华启蒙到2024年的智能引领，奔驰E级在豪华车领域的地位目前依然难以撼动。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">而在中国这个全球最大的汽车消费市场，奔驰E级车更是将本土化做到了极致，从设计到技术再到用户体验，每一步都精准切中需求，奔驰E级也用近20年的时间完成了从“客人”到“佼佼者”的蜕变。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">这不仅是一款车的成功，更是奔驰品牌在中国市场深耕细作的缩影，因此你就不难理解为何奔驰E级总是出现在友商的PPT当中了。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">在这个意义上，“靶心”不仅是后来者的挑战，也是对领先者的认可，更是行业地位的象征。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;">要想成为行业领跑者，首先得向奔驰E级看齐；而奔驰E级的传奇，也正是在无数次“被对标”的过程中，一次又一次地重新被续写。</span></p><p><strong class="js_darkmode__49" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(178, 178, 178);text-indent: 2em;font-family: PingFangTC-Light;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">*免责声明：在任何情况下，本文中的信息或所表述的意见，均不构成对任何人的投资建议。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p></article><p style="display: none;margin-bottom: 24px;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p> <p><a href="2247645323">阅读原文</a></p> <p><a href="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/link-proxy/?k=45e36718&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzUyNzcxNTgxOQ%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247645323%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D38363d22048c5e723c13dfb2bc103c7a%26chksm%3Dfa77a40fcd002d19c9f8a22fceb2b6fba1aabddbced99fb428320350ab1ac810caca46980b6e%26scene%3D58%26subscene%3D0%23rd">跳转微信打开</a></p> ]]>
