<title>忍不了“穷鬼减肥”，年轻人网上抢“神药”</title>
<link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzcxNTgxOQ==&mid=2247645315&idx=1&sn=aa3e40b37bcfb0e1b20be95dc024b4e8&chksm=fa77a407cd002d11d5bd0102352090113c766186c8814feb3939647e6185919f1ea06a0e49d0&scene=58&subscene=0#rd</link>
<description>头部药企展开线上渠道争夺战。</description>
