<title>2000个“产品经理”，帮字节做豆包</title>
<link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzcxNTgxOQ==&mid=2247645303&idx=1&sn=180a55cb00b3a62ce0e165f484857757&chksm=fa77a4f3cd002de5516624146f7870182badecd7cfa02f2e82a3381551c10fa539867a4b250e&scene=58&subscene=0#rd</link>
