<content:encoded>
<![CDATA[ <p> <span>凤凰网科技</span> <span>2024-11-27 18:30</span> <span style="display: inline-block;">北京</span> </p> <p>第一拨受益者已经出现了</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"> <img src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=8f68309f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FpxTUSmNgx78p1YIQ38uSe9gKE97SYjRuFjvm0ya8TCCLNu7UbFPXK1ibuRE65UvpbvX1gTvSavibJlrAicYE0GznQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg"/> </p> <p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 0px 8px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="279" data-backw="578" data-croporisrc="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/pxTUSmNgx78p1YIQ38uSe9gKE97SYjRuQ2yYXZWup1ZuELVkG9p3iaKHMCOlOLIfZUTqMYzqDpWCcC4jhexrHHQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-cropx1="0" data-cropx2="1820" data-cropy1="0" data-cropy2="878.5121107266436" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502300568" data-ratio="0.4824074074074074" data-s="300,640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=376778f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FpxTUSmNgx78p1YIQ38uSe9gKE97SYjRukOfsCJqjOaRxeeuufiaN5Q7tk46cqcntk7YCGqWICSE4W2wUuKibSHew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg"/></p><h3 data-foldable-wrapper="" data-style="outline: currentcolor none 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &#34;system-ui&#34;, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); visibility: visible; color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;" class="js_darkmode__0" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);visibility: visible;color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;"><p><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"></span></p><p style="margin: 8px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;"><span data-style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); outline: 0px; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; visibility: visible;" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;">导语：</span></strong><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;"><span data-style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); outline: 0px; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; visibility: visible;" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 1px;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 8px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;"><span data-style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); outline: 0px; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; visibility: visible;" style="font-size: 15px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;"><span class="js_darkmode__3" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">基于用新内容撬动新用户增长的思路，小红书是主动抓住这轮AI热，官方引入了一大批AI赛道创作者。与此同时，其官方也在下场研发相关产品与应用，不做生成式AI的局外人。</span></strong></span></strong></span></p></h3><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">凤凰网科技《新视界》出品</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">作者｜王丹宇</span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="color:#444444;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">编辑｜<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">董雨晴</span></span></span></strong></span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 24px 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="73" data-backw="562" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="502274141" data-ratio="0.12962962962962962" data-s="300,640" style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#34;Helvetica Neue&#34;, &#34;PingFang SC&#34;, &#34;Hiragino Sans GB&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei UI&#34;, &#34;Microsoft YaHei&#34;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 100%;height: auto;" data-type="png" data-w="1080" src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=17f2e47e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpxTUSmNgx7ibbqs9IPuyicNS6K4f2JPWPuyHhEuTamzPu5uulhRYAXFqtiaj8akPoCu2Z8NUMicT1C64XUowzFeTcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg"/></p><p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 24px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;">AI包围小红书</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 16px;">近来，不少小红书用户愈来愈多感受到平台上AI内容的含量。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 16px;">一大批虚拟AI账号正在小红书上崛起，他们往往带有“虚拟女友”、“赛博天使”等类似的账号介绍，即便有些图片中会有平台“疑似包含AI创作信息”的标注，但仍有大量的用户与其进行互动，包括赞美以及针对妆容、服装，乃至照片滤镜的“求同款”。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 16px;">这些AI图片的制作技术也已逐渐成熟，贴近真人的皮肤质感以及故意保留的细节瑕疵，都使其达到真假难辨的效果，<strong>这或许就是AI美女账号在小红书平台上获流容易，且难以遏制的原因。</strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 16px;">因此还涌现了一个独特的“AI打假赛道”，即找出那些通过了平台审核却没有声明自己的图片来自于AI生成的“假博主”，并讲解如何分辨真人和AI图片，其中包括观察图片“有没有眼神光”等技巧。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 24px 8px;"><strong><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 16px;">除了AI美人，更有靠批量生产鸡汤文学走红的“AI奶奶”们，借助工具生成一组动漫奶奶形象，再让大模型列举一些清醒语录、大女主发言、温暖治愈话术等文案，借助简单的图片制作工具将二者结合后，就可以成功制造数位AI奶奶，在吸引到一定的流量后，就可以通过卖货、发广告等形式实现变现。</span></strong><span style="font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;color: 