<title>一边骂一边买，中产仍在买爆山姆</title>
<link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzcxNTgxOQ==&mid=2247645299&idx=1&sn=1306a9414e0a205c9d76f5f3aa79b2a6&chksm=fa77a4f7cd002de1e0c213aa94587c9d7707b02d32abbd306078eea0ab1532d4544746a74a87&scene=58&subscene=0#rd</link>
<description>让人又爱又恨的山姆，仍被中产买爆。</description>
