<![CDATA[ <p> <span>吴文武</span> <span>2024-11-15 18:31</span> <span style="display: inline-block;">北京</span> </p> <p>汉堡王再不改变，只会更难。</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"> <img src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=619cbcb4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibNkISmqpY6yzf6J8B3ia4LIhNXma0KopQGCjpP2CwE9u4AwZJxDJ40hxB08B4dRDV1uHP4BVEXMYlv1F7lcW8IQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg"/> </p> <p style="letter-spacing: normal;white-space: normal;margin-right: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 10px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="343" data-backw="548" data-croporisrc="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibNkISmqpY6yzf6J8B3ia4LIhNXma0KopQsI03fTLcbg1GGLLR4Kot8pbj2Iw3t0pd0Utsgq2tHJhT848OlqAw2Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-cropx1="0" data-cropx2="1280" data-cropy1="53.72262773722628" data-cropy2="852.5547445255476" data-imgfileid="100005579" data-ratio="0.625" data-s="300,640" style="text-align: center;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 100%;height: auto !important;" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" src="https://wechat2rss-production-97e8.up.railway.app/img-proxy/?k=ce34a129&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibNkISmqpY6yzf6J8B3ia4LIhNXma0KopQSxkwiazibM6v3Z82ib6m9uqtYxRK3ypkJ2XxyeEt8rAusibQ63FIpWNkGw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg"/></p><p style="margin-right: 10px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 10px;padding: 16px;overflow-wrap: normal;overflow: auto;line-height: 1.45;border-radius: 3px;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(32, 32, 32);font-family: PingFangTC-Light;font-size: 16px;"><strong>汉堡王再不改变，只会更难。<span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0