<title>双11品牌复苏，中产又杀回来了？</title>
<link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzcxNTgxOQ==&mid=2247645286&idx=1&sn=19bfabcc848b58dc5ace56429a1b5b7e&chksm=fa77a4e2cd002df4ac7938f713c1a05a4587b9da41671314c5cfcff7ef8109479faee3585e43&scene=58&subscene=0#rd</link>
<description>中产不会真的抛弃品牌</description>
