<title>中国大模型在迪拜卷起来了</title>
<link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzcxNTgxOQ==&mid=2247645270&idx=1&sn=9cf7ed9423758c8760467fafb74494be&chksm=fa77a4d2cd002dc41ad5b2d99a36ea2736fab5ae34622c510c4515c294af8d6bf940669f12bc&scene=58&subscene=0#rd</link>
<description>迪拜是一个枢纽</description>
